data.description: Must sell!! Gorgeous 8.27 acreage property, with stunning home site view. Two tax IDs. Buckner creek runs through it. Gated and private. Lower area is level and great for your farm animals, horses currently there grazing now! Huge, huge shop, on slab, interior of shop has office space and multiple 220 outlets. Home is in need of repair or replace it with your dream home! No HUD sticker. Motivated seller looking for best offer.
